==Korean==
===Adverb===
'''같이''' (gachi)
#with, together
#:선생님과 '''같이''' 기념 사진을 찍었다 "We took a commemorative photo '''with''' our teacher." 
#like, in a similar way
#:형제'''같이''' 사이가 좋다. "They are as close '''as''' brothers" (literally "The relationship is as good as one between brothers".)

==Related terms==
#[[같이하다]] to do something together, to share

